{
  "stem": "2002.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would have to go to a train and take off 20-- 20 loads of wheat and bring it to-- to a mill where they make flours-- flour.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we always had something to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had to know this, [INAUDIBLE] told me all the time what I have to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, now I'm gonna go-- it's interesting enough, but I am rushing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm driving once with three trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I want to smoke a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the wind is blowing, and I cannot light the cigarette.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I stop in a site just to light the cigarette.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other two trucks go in in the front of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as they went in the front of me 1,000 feet, they were burning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans were on the top on the hill, and they were bombing the two trucks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I turned around, and I went back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was my lifesaving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK, one time we went in with the trucks to pick up a kitchen, another group of military, and move it to another section.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went in there and not knowing that the German army surrounded that place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever drove a car or a truck, and the more you want to run away, the-- the slower the truck goes because you're overflowing the gas in the-- in the truck.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I back in to a-- a wooden fence to get out, and I went out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of the 18 trucks, about six of them survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other [? one ?] was-- was cut off and-- and destroyed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lot of coincidence like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you had a lot of--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where they bombed the bridges--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very close.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One time, I am in a truck--",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
